welcome_message_body: Welcome to Natick, a charming city known for its beautiful parks, historic sites, and friendly community. We are thrilled to have you here and invite you to explore and experience all that Natick has to offer. Enjoy your stay!

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Hanscom Field Airport serves both commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Hanscom Field Airport caters to private and chartered flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Terminal A
terminals.description: The oldest and largest terminal at Logan International Airport, serving domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal B
terminals.description: A modern terminal with a variety of dining and shopping options, serving primarily domestic flights.

terminals.name: Terminal C
terminals.description: A recently renovated terminal with a focus on international flights, featuring high-end shopping and dining options.

terminals.name: Terminal E
terminals.description: The newest and most technologically advanced terminal at Logan International Airport, serving all international flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport, but may require signing in with an email address.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Memorial Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Memorial Airport is reserved for private and chartered flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Worcester Regional Airport serves all commercial flights.

terminals.name: General Aviation Terminal
terminals.description: The general aviation terminal at Worcester Regional Airport serves private and charter flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: This is the main terminal of North Central Airport, serving domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal handles all freight and cargo operations at North Central Airport.

wifi.note: Free wifi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Beverly Municipal Airport, serving domestic flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
